## Exercise 2 — Method Overriding (Easy–Medium)

Create a `Shape` class with an `area()` method that prints `"Area not defined"`.
Override `area()` in child classes `Circle` and `Rectangle` with actual calculations.

```
Expected Output:
Circle Area: 78.5
Rectangle Area: 24
```

